{"tid":540493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★90後I.T男創業 3年可半退休環遊世界","createTime":"2018-01-25T14:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T05:06:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cff89704081b514c71a04408d937038e3d8ab8cf","tid":540493,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"Jack畢業於浸會大學物理及電腦科學系，其後隨即進入大公司做電腦程式員，他戲稱是大眾形容的「I.T狗」。 事實上，Jack口中的「I.T狗」月入不俗，初入職雖然月薪只是約10,000元水平，但工作兩至三年後，月入已逾20,000元。<br />\n<br />\n原來他口中的「I.T狗」並非指收入低，而是每日做到像狗一樣，但為公司寫了不少的程式後，他認為沒有甚麼得著，得益的只是公司而非他。<br />\n<br />\n他認為這樣的工作是自討沒趣，故萌生自己在外創業的念頭。 由於Jack發現普羅大眾較難自學電腦程式，當時一個在General Assembly上課的電腦程式課程，收費動輒高達10萬元，故他認為或可照辦煮碗。<br />\n<br />\n014年他自行建立一個網頁，同時命名為鬍子科技學院，在網上提供一些簡單網頁設計的教學，不收分文。 另一方面，列出他可以提供的網頁設計課程資料，讓對網頁設計有更多興趣的人報讀。<br />\n<br />\n當時，Jack並沒有即時租用上課的場地，反而詢問開設公司的朋友借用辦公室，讓他可在週末有課堂時使用，且可以於實際開班時才繳付租金。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，Jack盡量減低其創業成本，他指因最初創業時難以確保必定能成功，故壓縮成本是最重要的一環。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.edigest.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/1872awin02_24961133859bba72ab1ee0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.edigest.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F1872awin02_24961133859bba72ab1ee0.png&h=a6971789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJack在創業成功後，出版著作《90後的半退休生活》，結合其創業過程中發現的創業竅門。<br />\n<br />\n現時不少就讀電腦科技的人的創業夢，是開發手機應用程式（App），但寫一個App的成本並不低，倘若開發及推出App後，發現無人問津，基本上本金都「凍過水」。<br />\n<br />\n因此，Jack建議有意開發App的人士，可先在社交媒體如Facebook，或其他網上渠道介紹App的內容。 假如反應熱烈，可再向有意使用該App的人交流，了解潛在用家的意見，覺得有發展空間才進行集資開發。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/workplace/%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%90%B5%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A515000%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B4000%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD%E8%B3%BA%E5%A4%A0/19/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2Fworkplace%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%2590%25B5%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A515000%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E6%25A8%2593-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B4000%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A0%2F19%2F&d=mBckM7UUbg0EyCBurPNnjmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b8a1153f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/workplace/%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%90%B5%E9%8C%A2%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A515000%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93-%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B4000%E5%89%B5%E6%A5%AD%E8%B3%BA%E5%A4%A0/19/</a>"},{"pid":"3f30350a3b70e884f80fecc0663a1a82b43145e6","tid":540493,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:18:50.000Z","msg":"book saleing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b3656f1d8013efff00755e6875e1597f06b90d","tid":540493,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"吹水佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40db88bb53d66a1d1471d4ccceb5d86dfdb1f838","tid":540493,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:21:52.000Z","msg":"more better<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/222136_00cab36cf8620b63171711cf02412a3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F222136_00cab36cf8620b63171711cf02412a3f.png&h=cb34d8eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"344cf3914d6770834ab7e994524165e3a22e3bb2","tid":540493,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"原來他口中的「I.T狗」並非指收入低，而是每日做到像狗一樣，但為公司寫了不少的程式後，他認為沒有甚麼得著，得益的只是公司而非他。<br />\n<br />\n睇下香港用 windows, mac 唔用 linux 個 d 人就見到呢個狀況"},{"pid":"fa5e4acc77a55796390f15118bf9327480eac24e","tid":540493,"uid":54684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"老貓呢期有無食魚柳早餐，我聽日想食呢個，推唔推介<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1510000/1511029/IMG_4954_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1510000%2F1511029%2FIMG_4954_1024.JPG&h=4d277dd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96f5125e5fb2b23abfdbc06149540fa1752d6919","tid":540493,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當時，Jack並沒有即時租用上課的場地，反而詢問開設公司的朋友借用辦公室，讓他可在週末有課堂時使用，且可以於實際開班時才繳付租金。與此同時，Jack盡量減低其創業成本，他指因最初創業時難以確保必定能成功，故壓縮成本是最重要的一環。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n創業有呢個意識, 真係難得<br />\n<br />\n100% correct"},{"pid":"ae62812edf7ea158fddbca5096441719e2e28f34","tid":540493,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"90後美少女參選立法會，三日可以退休"},{"pid":"1b20182c8676348078383bc47283abe66f2724f8","tid":540493,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fa5e4acc77a55796390f15118bf9327480eac24e","tid":540493,"uid":54684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"老貓呢期有無食魚柳早餐，我聽日想食呢個，推唔推介<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1510000/1511029/IMG_4954_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1510000%2F1511029%2FIMG_4954_1024.JPG&h=4d277dd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:34:14.000Z","msg":"kfc 有$2優惠，just用手機show就ok<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/25/223411_4ccd5cb5b7480f45b4baafec38037534.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F25%2F223411_4ccd5cb5b7480f45b4baafec38037534.png&h=8ee0dba5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa3c11deaa6f6fa5246bcf8ca9a3e4e8c0e3c2a4","tid":540493,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"IT 狗最唔會俾錢IT product/service <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e954b10fab37e